import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"kubectl-overview"}}>{`Kubectl Overview`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"setting-config"}}>{`Setting config`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Example exporting to set the correct `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`KUBECONFIG`}</MDXTag>{`.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-shell"}}>{`export KUBECONFIG=~/.kube/eksctl/clusters/cluster
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"base-fetching"}}>{`Base fetching`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Action`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Command`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Rolebindings`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get rolebinds --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=`}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<selector>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Pods`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get pods --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=`}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<selector>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Deployments`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get deployments --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=`}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<selector>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Services`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get svc --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=`}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<selector>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Replica Sets`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get replicasets --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=`}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<selector>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"all"}}>{`All`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Action`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Command`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Get rolebindings`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get all --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag>{` --selector=k8s-app=kubernetes-dashboard`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"rolebindings"}}>{`Rolebindings`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Action`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Command`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Get rolebindings`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl get rolebindings --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Describe rolebindings`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl describe rolebindings --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Describe rolebindings for service`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`kubectl describe rolebindings `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<service account>`}</MDXTag>{` --namespace `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="td">{`<namespace>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"services"}}>{`Services`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"pods"}}>{`Pods`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"deployments"}}>{`Deployments`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"replica-sets"}}>{`Replica Sets`}</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
